title: Roads Untraveled
description:
Marcus and Grayson of RoadsUntraveled are on a So-Cal road trip and came to talk about cars, tracks, S. American road trips and lots more. Roads Untraveled is a YouTube channel hosted by Marcus Vandenburg, showcasing the coolest cars that Canada (mostly) has to offer, and they have a lot. They get all the cool stuff we don't.  

This show is available as a video! https://youtu.be/-nliGz543Cg
